# MAINTENANCE.log - Project Maintenance History

## 2026-03-23
- **Summary:** Added standalone drone physics engine, flight scenario, 3D visualization, and runner script.
- **Actions:**
    - Created `drone_physics.py`: Quadrotor rigid-body physics engine with gravity, thrust, aerodynamic drag, attitude dynamics (rotation matrix + angular velocity + torque), ground constraint, SVD re-orthogonalization, and cascaded PID position controller. No ROS 2 dependency.
    - Created `drone_scenario.py`: Flight scenario — takeoff to 10m, fly through 4 waypoints, return to origin, land. Saves `scenario_data.npz`.
    - Created `visualize_drone_3d.py`: Dark-themed matplotlib 3D animated visualization with drone body-frame axes (attitude), velocity vector, ground shadow, waypoint markers, and altitude/speed/thrust timeline panels. Auto-runs simulation if no data file present.
    - Created `test_drone_physics.py`: 19 pytest tests covering rotation math, gravity freefall (analytical verification), ground constraint, hover equilibrium, aerodynamic drag, PID convergence, position controller, full simulation runs, and energy conservation.
    - Created `run_scenario.sh`: One-command runner script with `--test`, `--sim-only`, `--viz-only`, `--all` modes. Auto-creates venv and installs deps via `uv` or `pip`.
    - Fixed import paths in `drone_scenario.py` and `visualize_drone_3d.py` so they work when invoked from any directory.
    - Updated `AGENTS.md`: Added physics engine to simulation module docs, updated test instructions, added roadmap items for multi-drone physics and wind model.
    - Updated `README.md`: Added Quick Start section for standalone simulation, updated project structure tree, tech stack table, and test instructions.
    - Updated `TESTING.md`: Added 19 physics tests to test catalog with detailed descriptions per test.
    - Updated `sar_simulation/README.md`: Rewrote from placeholder to full module documentation.
- **Test Status:**
    - `drone_physics` (Python): 19/19 Pass
    - `sar_perception` (Python): 13/13 Pass
    - `sar_simulation` (Python): 1/1 Pass
    - `sar_swarm_control` (Rust): 17/17 (previously verified in ROS 2 env)
    - `heavy_lift_core` (Rust): 1/1 (previously verified)
    - **Total: 51 tests across all modules**

